title: President Donald J. Trump Is Working to Stop Evictions and Protect Americans’ Homes During the COVID-19 Pandemic – The White House
content:

I want to make it unmistakably clear that I’m protecting people from evictions.
						President Donald J. Trump					TEMPORARILY HALTING EVICTIONS: President Donald J. Trump is taking action to put a temporary halt to evictions during the COVID-19 pandemic.
